{"tid":1544536,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"907無論入唔入機場拍戲，你都要記住你係一個臨記","createTime":"2019-09-05T14:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T03:40:35.000Z","uid":54323,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"803a3748f90b873f94a1bab1b3d60b8c4294f084","tid":1544536,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"首先，係907果日，只要你出黎參與拍戲，你就係一個臨記<br />\n所以：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">精神D，臨時演員都係演員嚟</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BFAB6tTA8Gg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBFAB6tTA8Gg&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWK%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=b73a74b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BFAB6tTA8Gg</a><br />\n<br />\n果日既角色包括：<br />\n1. 旅客(就黎去旅行)<br />\n2. 旅客(去完旅行番黎)<br />\n3. 送接機既親友<br />\n4. 遊車河/打卡/鐘意飛機/機場/機場消費/散心...唔打落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果日既角色<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不</span></span></strong>包括：<br />\n1. 示威者<br />\n2. 仲係示威者<br />\n3. 都係示威者<br />\n<br />\n作為一個專業既臨記，要時常保持專業意識<br />\n以臨記既「專業判斷」黎決定你既行動<br />\n尤其不能忘記自己角色<span style=\"color: red;\">走左去做容易被誤認為另一角色既行為</span><br />\n例如唔會：<br />\n- 叫口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 上Gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 衝出馬路set RB<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等等<br />\n<br />\n成功係留比有準備既人，唔好以為臨記唔洗下功夫研究角色同磨練演技<br />\n希望以後個個禮拜人人都有戲拍有飯開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a1a2aa0290eac0f43967f35d4234341f93c04f","tid":1544536,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:00:22.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 出咗不反對啦！【9月6 反濫捕 抗威權 遮打集會】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543083</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂]9.